Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:32.67,0:01:40.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人类因人口膨胀而向宇宙移民已过了半个世纪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.26,0:01:43.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,地球周围漂浮着巨大的人工都市
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.71,0:01:45.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,作为人类的“第二故乡”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.37,0:01:52.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人们就在这里出生、成长、生儿育女\N并走向死亡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.59,0:02:00.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,宇宙世纪0079年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.71,0:02:03.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,离地球最远的宇宙都市SIDE 3
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.51,0:02:04.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以ZION公国之名
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.57,0:02:08.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,向地球联邦政府发起了独立战争
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.13,0:02:11.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在开始一个月的战斗里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.35,0:02:16.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,ZION公国和地球联邦军有半数以上的人口死去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.23,0:02:23.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人们对于自己的行为产生了恐惧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.93,0:02:35.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,‘飞吧！GUNDAM’
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.39,0:02:56.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第3班的人，请到餐厅用膳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.56,0:02:59.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对了，要去叫阿姆罗呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.90,0:03:06.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆罗！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.03,0:03:07.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,吃饭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.90,0:03:08.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆罗！吃饭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.22,0:03:09.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆罗！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.81,0:03:10.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆罗！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.51,0:03:19.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你做什么！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.95,0:03:21.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我没事！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.88,0:03:22.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你发烧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.75,0:03:23.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.88,0:03:25.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你这么疲倦还是不要去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.05,0:03:28.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,自从在卫星7号逃亡后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.46,0:03:30.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就从未好好的休息过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.93,0:03:34.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算我现在感觉很倦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.39,0:03:35.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是还睡不着...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.86,0:03:38.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要不要雪拉看看呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.87,0:03:41.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她好像学过点医学呢！是不是？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.67,0:03:43.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你别麻烦我好吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.34,0:03:44.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你要适可宜止啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.97,0:03:46.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一点不似平时的你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.37,0:03:47.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不停的在机动战士内作战的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.91,0:03:49.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,更不似平时的我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.58,0:03:51.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,上次战争那些大人大半也牺牲了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.08,0:03:55.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只靠少年人及老人来支持大局
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.28,0:03:58.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,相信联邦和ZION也是一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.01,0:04:01.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别咬手指！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.96,0:04:05.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,似乎联邦军将我们当做鱼饵...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.13,0:04:07.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鱼饵？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.29,0:04:12.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,联邦军一定在开发新武器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.47,0:04:14.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在这段期间就将我们作饵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.37,0:04:16.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去吸引敌军
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.24,0:04:19.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定是这样的！我们...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.41,0:04:20.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你别乱想了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.87,0:04:21.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还是先休息一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.11,0:04:23.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我为你留起食物好吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.81,0:04:26.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,气死人！还未联络到总部？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.85,0:04:28.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有无线电来了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.65,0:04:30.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,参谋总部吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.49,0:04:30.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好极了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.25,0:04:32.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,总部，这里是母舰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.89,0:04:36.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请将通信由M转去Z路线
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.11,0:04:38.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Z路线吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.21,0:04:38.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.03,0:04:46.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希望母舰可以冲出敌军包围
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.93,0:04:48.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,向着大海方向走出去？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.94,0:04:50.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就只有这些
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.37,0:04:52.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,连如何支持也没提及？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.51,0:04:55.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那...我们不可和总部通话吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.38,0:04:56.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不能！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.54,0:05:00.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在敌军范围用暗号通信己很危险
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.38,0:05:03.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,参谋本部是如何想的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.52,0:05:05.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们根本不知什么是战场！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.82,0:05:06.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,田村先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.19,0:05:08.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老人家们的食物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.92,0:05:12.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,当然啊！我们又没法找到证据
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.96,0:05:16.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,胡说！以为我在收起自己吃吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.02,0:05:17.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果不是的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.66,0:05:19.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么你的面色会比我们好呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.47,0:05:20.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,岂有此理！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.20,0:05:22.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我问你吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.00,0:05:24.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,何以阿姆罗和良的膳食
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.04,0:05:27.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,会在份量上多出那么多的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.31,0:05:28.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是布莱特的指示
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.91,0:05:31.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他是要将俩人当作正规军看待！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.01,0:05:32.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我吃饱了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.05,0:05:34.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,又不是只有他们去打仗！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.45,0:05:37.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,军人的食物是以工作量计算的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.92,0:05:40.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,凯，别吵了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.75,0:05:44.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样的事可以和队长说吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.42,0:05:45.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谁会理我呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.20,0:05:52.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆罗哥，我给你一样东西？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.00,0:05:55.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你要加油啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.29,0:05:56.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.31,0:06:00.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别让人知道呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.21,0:06:01.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.55,0:06:10.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,母舰的武器和弹药快用尽了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.88,0:06:13.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下次敌人来还可捱得住吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.62,0:06:17.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也知道！所以正在想法子呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.76,0:06:19.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,若想生存下去，还不简单！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.09,0:06:21.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别开玩笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.73,0:06:23.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要放弃White Base
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.53,0:06:25.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,李中尉...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.20,0:06:30.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你竟然这么想？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.67,0:06:32.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别放在心上啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.18,0:06:46.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们一起吃吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.52,0:06:48.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那怎样好意思啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.39,0:06:49.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,多谢了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.89,0:06:52.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆罗！你不吃怎可以？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.86,0:06:54.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那便别叫我在这里吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.76,0:06:56.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆罗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.86,0:06:59.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样做有什么后果呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.57,0:07:01.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们可以一直战至今日？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.47,0:07:03.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,总算也有一点成绩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.29,0:07:07.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家也培养出单独作战的能力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.47,0:07:10.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,队长，破烂的地方大致上修好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.98,0:07:13.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隼人和雪拉去那里？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.48,0:07:14.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在调整瞄准器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.15,0:07:17.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,找人出去巡逻一下吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.65,0:07:22.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆罗，你去做巡逻工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.72,0:07:23.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,上来控制室吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.39,0:07:27.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在做什么！上来啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.13,0:07:33.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆罗，快些上来！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.10,0:07:37.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,巡逻工作不必我去做吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.20,0:07:38.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.44,0:07:40.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我己经要时常作战
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.04,0:07:42.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不去！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.18,0:07:44.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆罗！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.98,0:07:46.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆罗实在很倦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.55,0:07:48.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们亦太过依懒他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.15,0:07:51.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还是由我和隼人出去巡逻吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.20,0:08:03.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,全部交给计算机控制！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.96,0:08:05.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好的！正打算这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.37,0:08:11.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好！现在先将部计算机调好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.24,0:08:12.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要它跟着我便成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.97,0:08:13.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.64,0:08:20.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,唔，你看！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.45,0:08:31.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡尔玛，其实你不需要去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.42,0:08:32.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.26,0:08:35.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要向姊姊交待的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.46,0:08:38.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没有家人的你是不会明白的了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.13,0:08:42.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,全员准备出发攻击！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.04,0:08:45.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么事呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.44,0:08:46.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是敌军战斗机
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.79,0:08:47.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.41,0:08:49.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡尔玛，立即停止攻击！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.41,0:08:50.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.91,0:08:53.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我现在就去击落他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.31,0:08:54.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,先回来，卡尔玛！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.98,0:08:58.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,良，费了不少努力才发现敌军
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.82,0:09:00.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么不立即攻击呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.39,0:09:05.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果我们有6架核战机早攻击了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.23,0:09:11.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是30秒前的影像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.10,0:09:14.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过只是一架巡逻机
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.70,0:09:16.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看来木马正十分焦急
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.17,0:09:18.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,焦急？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.81,0:09:20.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们是第一次派出巡逻机的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.01,0:09:26.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为有弱点所以才想知我们动静
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.45,0:09:27.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你说得有点道理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.81,0:09:29.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那不必去理会那巡逻机
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.88,0:09:31.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,应该立即攻击母舰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.95,0:09:33.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快！去追踪敌军的巡逻机
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.50,0:09:46.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好，准备将核战机安装到钢坦克及钢加农
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.86,0:09:47.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.47,0:09:55.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,又要入去铁棺材里！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.15,0:10:00.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我坐到上面去吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.01,0:10:02.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,良，拜托了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.32,0:10:03.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你要早给我指示呀！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.67,0:10:04.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.69,0:10:09.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我还以为你会了解我的心情...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.79,0:10:11.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我一点也不了解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.59,0:10:13.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,连凯也用钢加农出击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.03,0:10:15.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家也下定决心去作战
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.33,0:10:19.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很快大家就会不想去的了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.43,0:10:21.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我和他们不同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.37,0:10:24.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已经被命令出去很多次的了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.11,0:10:29.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么事？芙劳·波
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.71,0:10:30.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆罗不成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.26,0:10:32.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,说他不想去作战
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.46,0:10:32.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.41,0:10:34.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,队长！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.71,0:10:35.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆罗，你听着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.12,0:10:37.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在要应战了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.55,0:10:38.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你可以保证我作战后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.65,0:10:40.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,回来可好好睡一觉吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.69,0:10:41.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,保证？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.39,0:10:43.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆罗...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.72,0:10:46.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,事实我自己也不知该怎样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.03,0:10:51.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道..若没有阿姆罗你去作战
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.36,0:10:52.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们一早已经死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.27,0:10:56.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我自己也早死了..不过..
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.44,0:10:58.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这种事实在太恐怖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.25,0:11:12.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,平安降落...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.12,0:11:14.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,凯，去吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.68,0:11:15.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.29,0:11:20.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们就只有这点军力？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.23,0:11:21.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,队长先生？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.69,0:11:23.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,GUNDAM就快来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.70,0:11:26.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打仗要有信心才可取胜，对吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.43,0:11:27.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.02,0:11:30.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雪拉小姐真是善于帮别人壮胆！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.90,0:11:34.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆罗，你为何不出动完成任务？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.61,0:11:37.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请问队长为什么而要去打仗呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.88,0:11:41.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我现在根本没时间跟你讲哲学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.68,0:11:42.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快起来！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.15,0:11:44.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你别这样好吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.75,0:11:46.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果你真想GUNDAM出击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.65,0:11:48.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,何不自己来驾驶呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.62,0:11:49.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.86,0:11:52.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果我会驾驶，我早做了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.69,0:11:53.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不用你来说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.89,0:11:56.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也一样，并不是因为会才要去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.63,0:12:01.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你...你打我？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.83,0:12:03.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,布莱特队长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.47,0:12:05.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我打你有什么不对！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.21,0:12:07.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你自己想清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.67,0:12:09.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在大发脾气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.54,0:12:10.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就可以发泄得了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.31,0:12:14.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你以为我是个没出息的人？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.54,0:12:41.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那面又来了一队敌军
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.44,0:12:42.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,良，你要小心啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.38,0:12:47.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么？你叫我别太过前进？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.65,0:12:50.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隼人，这地方较空旷，要小心！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.75,0:12:51.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.22,0:12:55.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.76,0:12:57.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我明白敌军出了什么问题！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.76,0:12:59.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那太好了！为什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.13,0:13:01.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,告诉我好吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.46,0:13:02.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是那个机动战士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.73,0:13:04.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽然现在有两个陆战型出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.66,0:13:06.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但最利害的却没出现
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.33,0:13:07.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我看多数是故障！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.33,0:13:10.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由现在起你别插手看我的手段吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.67,0:13:12.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看我打败他们给你看！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.67,0:13:15.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我会好好见识你的高明攻击法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.05,0:13:22.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打中了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.28,0:13:24.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,将攻击的目标定在左引擎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.75,0:13:26.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,钢坦克，钢加农
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.39,0:13:28.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敌军正在集中火力攻击左引擎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.82,0:13:29.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快来掩护
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.82,0:13:33.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还要来！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.76,0:13:36.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这班家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.30,0:13:43.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不好！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.44,0:13:47.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你打了我两次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.11,0:13:50.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我爸爸也从来未动过手打我！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.51,0:13:52.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以你才会任性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.51,0:13:55.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,未经教训的人是不会长大过来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.02,0:13:59.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我绝对不会去，就算是以后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.02,0:14:01.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也不会再去驾驶GUNDAM的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.46,0:14:04.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆罗，你讲说话要适可而止！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.82,0:14:06.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你一定要振作过来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.26,0:14:08.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别再说那些无情的话！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.30,0:14:12.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要去控制室
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.77,0:14:14.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆罗！如果你还要任性下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.97,0:14:16.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是一个没出息的废物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.37,0:14:18.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,本来我以为你很有天份
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.41,0:14:20.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,会胜过夏亚，可以打败他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.71,0:14:23.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但你太令我失望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.54,0:14:25.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,夏亚！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.05,0:14:28.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,布莱特队长！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.38,0:14:28.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,布莱特队长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.97,0:14:30.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆罗！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.62,0:14:33.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我记得你有本驾驶GUNDAM的说明书
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.82,0:14:34.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.57,0:14:36.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要去驾驶GUNDAM！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.66,0:14:39.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我最讨厌没有自信的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.46,0:14:42.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,尤其是不敢说要保护母舰的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.10,0:14:45.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆罗，你不是男子汉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.13,0:14:48.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.24,0:14:50.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,芙劳·波...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.67,0:14:54.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,GUNDAM并不是容易驾驶的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.44,0:14:56.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆罗！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.24,0:14:58.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽然我仍不忿气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.98,0:15:02.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但我是男子汉！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.88,0:15:07.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆罗，你去那里！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.02,0:15:13.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,夏亚！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.46,0:15:18.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,良，敌人只攻击母舰，快回防
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.40,0:15:19.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.00,0:15:25.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只得两架机
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.17,0:15:27.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,若没有对空炮火的武器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.57,0:15:29.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,根本就打不中的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.78,0:15:35.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,听着，别理喽啰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.38,0:15:38.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,集中攻击木马的左边引擎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.32,0:15:39.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道！上校！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.69,0:15:40.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去吧，跟我来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.66,0:15:43.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆罗！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.82,0:15:47.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敌机正全力攻击左引擎！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.29,0:15:50.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你有办法对付他们吗？阿姆罗！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.06,0:15:54.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我有个新的战法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.50,0:15:56.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请叫钢坦克和钢加农掩护我好吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.20,0:15:58.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我会通知他们的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.57,0:15:59.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,靠你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.54,0:16:03.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡尔玛上校的攻击法看来相当高明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.78,0:16:06.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,似乎他并不是光靠父母的威望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.11,0:16:09.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就可以升高官的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.32,0:16:12.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少校，我们只看不帮手可以吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.19,0:16:15.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没事的，假如要帮手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.75,0:16:16.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他自会通知我们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.06,0:16:18.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,上校的自尊心很强
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.16,0:16:21.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,搞不好反而会被他痛骂！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.93,0:16:22.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以这个距离
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.03,0:16:25.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,相信无线电是可以接收到的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.66,0:16:28.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的！虽然粒子的浓度依然很强
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.67,0:16:30.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但现在的距离通信是没问题的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.37,0:16:34.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果可以联络的话就可以了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.04,0:16:36.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,事实上我也不愿意被卡尔玛上校骂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.28,0:16:45.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你这个机动战士终于也出来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.99,0:16:48.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,始终也是陆战用的武器！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.55,0:16:49.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第二小队
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.62,0:16:50.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,立即攻击白色机动战士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.59,0:16:53.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样就想打败我？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.09,0:16:55.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其实GUNDAM是藏着弹跳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.53,0:16:57.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和火箭式的冲力系统的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.97,0:17:04.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊！机动战士会飞的吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.74,0:17:05.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有机会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.64,0:17:08.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一架
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.91,0:17:09.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆罗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.29,0:17:11.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,GUNDAM竟可在空中作战？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.08,0:17:12.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.15,0:17:14.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,厉害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.48,0:17:17.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用无线电叫坦克及激光火炮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.78,0:17:20.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在GUNDAM落地之前掩护他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.39,0:17:21.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别令他让人袭击！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.95,0:17:23.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.69,0:17:25.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,钢坦克，钢加农
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.39,0:17:26.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以见到GUNDAM吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.53,0:17:27.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,早知道了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.56,0:17:30.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想不到阿姆罗这么利害！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.33,0:17:31.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隼人，去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.63,0:17:33.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.87,0:17:35.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要不让飞机低飞是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.64,0:17:39.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不会给你们飞低过一尺的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.47,0:17:44.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,8、5、0...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.61,0:17:50.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那机动战士会跳高的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.02,0:17:52.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不，是在飞行呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.99,0:17:55.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,联邦军竟然有这种机动战士？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.90,0:18:04.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,3架！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.41,0:18:19.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,队长，真想不到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.24,0:18:21.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆罗会有这种高飞的战术呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.21,0:18:22.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对，是那家伙的优点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.85,0:18:23.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽然口中说不愿意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.08,0:18:25.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但仍然和敌人周旋到底
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.02,0:18:29.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆罗！你变坚强了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.43,0:18:34.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看着吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.96,0:18:37.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第6架！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.72,0:18:38.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟着第7架！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.70,0:18:41.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第7架
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.54,0:18:52.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,司令机？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.95,0:18:57.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你这只怪物，掉下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.15,0:18:59.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快给我掉下去！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.22,0:19:03.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.03,0:19:13.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很利害！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.20,0:19:14.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,野牛！听到吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.29,0:19:15.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.87,0:19:18.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我现在将那机动战士引过来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.34,0:19:20.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,待他入到射程范围
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.04,0:19:22.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,立即开火！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.08,0:19:25.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不会让你逃的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.58,0:19:32.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他还不知快进入野牛的射程呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.02,0:19:35.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,野牛，快将他轰下来！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.79,0:19:40.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,听到吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.43,0:19:41.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,野牛！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.13,0:19:42.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是我！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.15,0:19:43.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡尔玛上校啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.53,0:19:51.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么？我的确在发出讯号啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.64,0:20:00.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,岂有此理！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.58,0:20:02.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.88,0:20:06.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是联邦的运输机？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.09,0:20:12.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在那边的机动战士，你听到吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.42,0:20:14.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,山中是埋有野牛的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.53,0:20:15.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快回White Base吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.90,0:20:18.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是谁呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.93,0:20:21.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么会知的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.90,0:20:22.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,电线松掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.14,0:20:25.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,当然会引致接触不良
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.67,0:20:28.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,技师长准备接受惩罚处分吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.18,0:20:31.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你究竟做什么呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.23,0:20:33.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.58,0:20:36.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你应该在屏幕看到我作战的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.45,0:20:37.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算我没通知你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.08,0:20:39.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也应该想办法来协助
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.89,0:20:43.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是因为我怕伤了你的自尊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.76,0:20:45.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怕伤害我的自尊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.66,0:20:47.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为你叫我别插手的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.83,0:20:49.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且我亦了解到像你这样的高手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.20,0:20:51.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只是轻微损伤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.00,0:20:54.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定可以在下次弥补到的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.70,0:20:56.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那当然！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.80,0:20:59.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过最可惜的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.64,0:21:01.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是当我要击落联邦军运输机时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.17,0:21:04.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,上校就在射程的直线上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.94,0:21:06.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,使我无法攻击！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.95,0:21:08.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很对不起！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.51,0:21:11.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不！你明白便好了！夏亚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.09,0:21:21.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,李中尉和密斯号来的队员
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.56,0:21:23.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,与及病人一共35人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.73,0:21:24.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们都愿意收留
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.96,0:21:28.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,至于White Base则没有任何指示
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.23,0:21:30.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以要维持原状
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:30.94,0:21:33.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,另外到目前的战斗纪录
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.24,0:21:35.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由于雷比尔将军的命令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.21,0:21:36.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请给我们一份影印本
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.51,0:21:38.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但玛吉露达少尉，我不明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.61,0:21:42.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么White Base要维持原状？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.68,0:21:45.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这点我不知道！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:45.62,0:21:47.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过雷比尔将军认为母舰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.49,0:21:48.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以战下去的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.79,0:21:50.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就可以拨入正规军行列
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:50.69,0:21:53.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为现在的联邦军内部正一团糟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:55.03,0:21:59.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我这次来，是奉了雷比尔将军之命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.70,0:22:02.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和参谋本部是没有关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:02.90,0:22:03.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那样...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:04.07,0:22:05.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,会再给我们援助吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:05.67,0:22:08.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不知道！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:08.24,0:22:10.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,离开ZION军的势力范围后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:10.31,0:22:11.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,或者可以的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:11.98,0:22:12.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,无论怎样也好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:13.15,0:22:14.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请别忘记联邦军内
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:15.15,0:22:17.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,仍有人关心你们的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:19.15,0:22:21.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,玛吉露达少尉...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:21.39,0:22:24.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果没有你这样英勇的作战
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:24.66,0:22:27.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也早就死了，很多谢你！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:28.19,0:22:30.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可能你是个超能力者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:31.20,0:22:32.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎会？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:33.40,0:22:33.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,加油啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:34.61,0:22:34.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:50.92,0:22:53.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,玛吉露达少尉留下一阵香味便走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:53.59,0:22:55.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对阿姆罗来说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:55.42,0:22:59.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还是初次体会女性的香味
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:17.17,0:23:21.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没能打下White Base也就无法和伊榭莲娜相爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:22.20,0:23:25.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡尔玛·萨比展开最后的突击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:26.35,0:23:28.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,当阿姆罗他们在黑暗中看到恐惧时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:29.16,0:23:31.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,夏亚的阴谋笼罩了卡尔玛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:33.04,0:23:34.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,机动战士GUNDAM
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:34.78,0:23:36.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下一集 ‘卡尔玛之死’
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:38.04,0:23:40.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你能够存活下去吗？

